# artwork
NativeScript artwork

## Color

| Name | RGB | HEX |
|------|-----|-----|
| NativeScript Blue | `rgb(101, 173, 241)` | `#65ADF1`

## Font

| Name | Font |
|------|------|
| NativeScript Logo | `Inter Black` | `#65ADF1`

## Logo Variants

There are different variants of the NativeScript logo available in png and svg formats.
